+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DyfVEMZUVAHgx2yQxLbECm","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! I now have a complete understanding of the monorepo. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Complete Monorepo Structure & Content Analysis\n\n### Repository Overview\n- **Type**: Monorepo with npm workspaces\n- **Name**: `bench-monorepo-disaster`\n- **Current State**: Detached HEAD at commit `ff809f6` (initial: v1 starting state)\n- **Packages**: 3 workspace packages (core, api, worker)\n- **TypeScript**: Enabled with strict mode and project references\n\n---\n\n## Root Configuration Files\n\n### `/workspace/package.json`\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-monorepo-disaster\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"description\": \"Monorepo recovery benchmark\",\n  \"workspaces\": [\"packages/*\"],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc -b\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint packages/*/src/ packages/*/tests/ tests/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\",\n    \"check:circular\": \"madge --circular --extensions ts packages/\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.56.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"madge\": \"^8.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### `/workspace/tsconfig.json`\n```json\n{\n  \"files\": [],\n  \"references\": [\n    { \"path\": \"packages/api\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/worker\" },\n    { \"path\": \"packages/core\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### `/workspace/.env`\n```\nDB_HOST=localhost\nDB_PORT=5432\nDB_USER=admin\nDB_PASSWORD=super_secret_password_123\nDB_NAME=monorepo_db\n```\n\n### `/workspace/.eslintrc.cjs`\n```javascript\nmodule.exports = {\n  parser: '@typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['eslint:recommended', 'plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecma